summary: This is an email communication regarding the technical production and delivery of documents in the US v. Epstein case, specifically referencing the SDNY_PROD015 production broken into multiple parts. It provides status updates on document processing and export.
keyFacts: Document references 'US v. Epstein' case and a production labeled SDNY_PROD015.
Vendor broke the document production into seven parts, with parts 1-3 completed and part 4 about to start.
Parts 1 and 2 were exported to a hard drive, with part 3 finished but not yet exported at the time of the email.
Email sent on November 4, 2020, providing a status update on document processing.
The communication is logistical, focusing on the technical delivery of case documents rather than substantive case details.
